articles.description: USC's Bennie Boatwright, who was averaging 13.6 points and 6.4 rebounds per game, is out for the season with a knee injury.
articles.headline: USC's Bennie Boatwright out for season with knee injury

articles.description: USC's investigation into the college basketball bribery scandal found no institutional neglect by its program. Athletic director Lynn Swann said then-assistant coach Tony Bland "was operating outside [the] boundaries."
articles.headline: USC probe finds no institutional neglect; Tony Bland acted 'outside boundaries'

articles.description: Gary Chivichyan set career highs with eight 3-pointers and 25 points, Jared Stutzman had four 3s and 20 points, including the go-ahead jumper with 41 seconds left, and Idaho State beat Sacramento State 67-60 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Idaho State hits 12 3s in 67-60 win over Sacramento State

articles.description: The Wildcats have owned the Big East, but recent losses have opened the door for the Musketeers to take the league, starting with Saturday's matchup.

articles.description: In a league as competitive as the Big 12, opportunities abound for quality wins. The problem, as Texas and Oklahoma are learning in recent weeks, is winning those games. Will the Longhorns or Sooners end their losing streaks this weekend?

articles.description: Gregg Marshall yells and screams. That's how he gets his point across. But he also listens. Amid an up-and-down year at Wichita State, the man whom bigger programs are always chasing will listen again.

videos.description: Duke's Marques Bolden gets the ball in the post and sinks a hook shot.
videos.headline: Bolden converts hook in the post

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie swings the ball over to Brandon Alston in the corner for a contested 3-pointer and the foul to earn a chance at a 4-point play.
videos.headline: Alston drains corner 3 for and-1 chance

videos.description: Duke's Wendell Carter Jr. gets the ball inside and spins by Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie for a loud two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Carter spins by Okogie for emphatic slam

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tadaric Jackson tries taking it inside for a layup but is rejected by Duke's Wendell Carter Jr.
videos.headline: Carter denies Jackson's lay-in attempt

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen splits through the defense and converts a layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Allen slices through defense for tough lay-in

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen lofts a pass up to Wendell Carter Jr. for an emphatic two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Allen connects with Carter on emphatic alley-oop

videos.description: Duke's Wendell Carter Jr. spins by his defender in the post to convert the layup.
videos.headline: Carter spins for post lay-in

videos.description: After missing his initial shot attempt, Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie grabs the offensive rebound and sinks a layup to earn the and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Okogie converts second-chance points for 3-point play

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie tries going up for a layup but his shot is stripped, deflected off his knee and off the backboard to set up Evan Cole's layup.
videos.headline: Okogie unintentionally sets up Cole's lay-in

videos.description: Following the miss from Georgia Tech's Josh Okogie, Moses Wright hauls in the offensive rebound and throws down an emphatic two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Wright throws down thunderous putback slam

videos.description: Grayson Allen finds Trevon Duval open in the corner for a 3 to extend Duke's lead.
videos.headline: Allen finds Duval for corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Following a missed 3-pointer from Georgia Tech's Tadric Jackson, Evan Cole comes out of nowhere and converts the emphatic two-handed slam, making him a #SCTop10 nominee.
videos.headline: Cole cleans up missed 3 with emphatic putback

videos.description: Without Marvin Bagley III, Grayson Allen and a slew of freshman defeat a struggling Georgia Tech team 80-69.
videos.headline: Duke rolls to victory over Georgia Tech
